==German==
===Etymology===
''[[treppe|Treppe]]n'' "stairs" + ''[[Witz]]'' "wit", lit. transl. of Fr. [[l'esprit de l'escalier]]

===Noun===
'''Treppenitz''' ''m''

# "Staircase wit", a devastating rejoinder thought of only after leaving the scene of the debate.

